column3: Suzanne Nicoll's wonderful custom vintage looking Enough Fishing image printed directly to a distressed looking wood panel with occasional knots and other natural characteristics. The panels are made from natural real wood slats. By printing over the natural characteristics each panel gains character and interest. This wall decor sign can be personalized with name drops. No two are the same!
